  }, "v2"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c s\u1EE9 gi\u1EA3 \u0111\u1EBFn b\xE1o c\xE1o c\xF9ng Gi\xF4-sa-ph\xE1t, \"M\u1ED9t \u0111\u1EA1o qu\xE2n r\u1EA5t l\u1EDBn t\u1EEB \xCA-\u0111\xF4m, t\u1EEB ph\xEDa b\xEAn kia Bi\u1EC3n Ch\u1EBFt, k\xE9o \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111\xE1nh vua. H\u1ECD \u0111\xE3 v\xE0o Ha-xa-x\xF4n Ta-ma!\" Ha-xa-x\xF4n Ta-ma c\u0169ng c\xF3 t\xEAn l\xE0 \xCAn-gh\xEA-\u0111i. "), mdx("h6", {
